- the ability to select, evaluate and apply a range of different teaching, learning and assessment methodologies in lesson presentation on aspects of the Middle East up to 0; and
- a reflection of all values of an ethical-professional nature and justifiable decision making in a diverse society appropriate in accordance with the context of the Manifest for Values, Education and
Democracy.

